ORA METROP NORT OCCIDEN TERRITORIAL UNIT COL

To perform detailed design and execute MV and LV works, managing related contracts, monitoring contractual performance and relative obligations (e.g. penalties application, etc.);
to execute emergency plans and faults management in coordination with Network Operation and Maintenance Colombia;
to execute maintenance programs, inspection on MV and LV networks;
to execute filed activities related to customers’ requests.

O&M PERFORMANCE MANAGEMENT & CONTROL COL

·To monitor and control economic and technical KPI, identifying significant gaps and possible corrective actions, in order to improve the business performance and operational efficiency for Operations and Maintenance processes, ensuring data quality management; to perfom network service quality indicator monitoring, ensuring the internal/external reporting liaising with Network Operations unit;

·to carry out operational analysis proposing possible improvement actions;

·to support Resource Allocation and Monitoring Unit for the process of budgeting, industrial planning, totex monitoring and improvement plan definition, liaising with Network Analysis and Solutions Optimization Unit, related to Operations and Maintenance processes.

O&M MAINTENANCE COLOMBIA

To manage the implementation of procedures and operating instructions on network maintenance, also defining training contents;

·To provide specialized maintenance competences for the Global network of expertise, providing technical assistance on maintenance issues;
